overview: A triumphant performance from the King of the Blues Guitar at the Theatre Antique,Vienne,France 1988.  Includes:  Got My Mojo Working,Five Long Years,Someone Else Is Steppin In Slippin Out,Slippin In,Shes Nineteen Years Old,Strange Brew ,Mustang Sally,Voodoo Chile,Red House,Midnight Train,Sweet Home Chicago.
title: Buddy Guy - Slippin in
